Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LineDrawer
    class that when created draws a 100 lines on the container and then clears it out and draws them again and just keeps continuously drawing.
    ScreenSaver
    When object of ScreenSaver class is created, an invisible frame is created where the LineDrawer object will draw 100 lines and then clear the screen and start over continuously in a container with a black background.
    ScreenSaverImplementation
    ScreenSaverImplementation class that implements the ScreenSaver class in the main function by creating an object, calling the setSize method to set the size of the window to pop up, and then makes the ScreenSaver Object visible using the setVisible method and passing in true.
